  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "fa37c48f-76f4-46eb-b92b-8d0f7e221d1c",
    "name": "MCD - Den Glade Skorpe",
    "description": "## Run order\n\n**Rules**\n- Run SignIn first — saves `{{token}}`\n- Run Dishes before Orders — Post Order depends on `{{dish_id}}`\n- Within each folder: run POST/create first, then GET / PUT / DELETE\n\n**Execution order**\n1. Auth → SignIn → Token Check\n2. Users → Add User → Get User ID → Update User → Delete User\n3. Dishes → Post Dish → Get Dish By ID → Update Dish → Delete Dish By ID\n4. Orders → Post Order → Update Order → Delete Order By ID\n5. Messages → Post Message → Update Message → Delete Message\n6. Ingredients → Post/Create Ingredient → Put/Update Ingredient → Delete Ingredient By ID\n7. Employees → Post/Create Employee → Get Employee By ID → Update Employee → Delete Employee\n8. Categories → Create Category → Update Category → Delete Category By ID\n\n**Variable map**\n| Request | Saves |\n|---|---|\n| SignIn | `{{token}}` |\n| Add User | `{{user_id}}` (pre-req generates unique `{{test_email}}`) |\n| Post Dish | `{{dish_id}}` |\n| Post Message | `{{message_id}}` |\n| Post Order | `{{order_id}}` |\n| Post/Create Ingredient | `{{ingredient_id}}` |\n| Post/Create Employee | `{{employee_id}}` |\n| Create Category | `{{category_id}}` |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "38584738",
    "_collection_link": "https://mcdmviborg.postman.co/workspace/webmcdm.dk---Server-Projects~f1ca1e4d-4cb3-49f6-9664-7a010d498024/collection/17346811-fa37c48f-76f4-46eb-b92b-8d0f7e221d1c?action=share&source=collection_link&creator=38584738"
  },
